    <h1>Getting Started</h1>
    <p>While every component has a particular scss file, all styleguide related scss files are compiled into one master file <code>style.css</code>. This represents all patterns, mixins, variables, and component styles.</p>

    <p>Buoy also includes javascript, which is responsible for some components such as chosen-select boxes and patterns such as modals or input float labels. This javascript is included in the ruby gem.</p>

